<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<meta name="author" content="Untree.co">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.png">
	<meta name="description" content="Dr. Mohammed Ghalwash - Pioneer in Hair Restoration and Microsurgery" />
	<meta name="keywords" content="plastic surgery, hair restoration, microsurgery, alexandria" />

	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Brygada+1918:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/fonts/icomoon/style.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/fonts/flaticon/font/flaticon.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tiny-slider.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aos.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/flatpickr.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/glightbox.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

	<title>Dr. Mohammed Ghalwash - Pioneering Microsurgery</title>

	<style>
		@media (max-width: 1000px) {
			.moving-background {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
				position: relative;
			}
			.content-of-moving-background {
				position: absolute;
				left: 50%;
				top: 50%;
				transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
				text-align: center;
			}
			.button-of-moving-background {
				display: inline-block;
				margin-top: 10px;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 700px) {
			.heading-pages h1 {
				font-size: 29px;
				line-height: 1.2;
			}
			.heading-pages p {
				font-size: 14px;
			}
			.heading-pages a {
				font-size: 14px;
			}
			.align-items-center {
				width: 100% !important;
			}
		}

		.align-items-center {
			width: 80%;
		}
		.container, .container4, .container5 {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}
		.info {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateX(100%);
			transition: all 1s ease-out;
		}
		.info.active {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateX(0);
		}
		.text-section p, .col-lg-5 p {
			text-align: justify;
			text-justify: inter-word;
			font-size: 17px;
			color: black;
		}
		.accordion-item {
			border: 1px solid #d3d3d3;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	{{> header}}

	<div class="heading-pages">
		<h1>Meet Dr. Mohammed</h1>
		<p><a href="/">Home</a> > About > Meet Dr. Mohammed</p>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center">
				<div class="col-lg-5 mb-4 mb-lg-0 order-lg-2" data-aos="fade-up">
					<img src="/images/img-1.jpg" alt="Dr. Mohammed Ghalwash" class="img-fluid">
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
					<h2 class="heading mb-4">A Pioneer's Journey in Restorative Surgery</h2>
					<p>Born on July 14, 1964, Dr. Mohammed Ghalwash began his surgical journey with a profound mission: restoring hope and dignity to his patients. For over four decades, his skilled hands have transformed thousands of lives through innovative surgical techniques.</p>
					<p>From pioneering follicular unit transplantation in Saudi Arabia to revolutionizing microsurgery in Egypt, Dr. Ghalwash has maintained an unwavering commitment to surgical excellence and patient care.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section bg-light">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-5 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
					<img src="/images/doc.jpg" alt="Dr. Mohammed in Surgery" class="img-fluid">
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-7">
					<div class="custom-accordion" id="accordion_1">
						<div class="accordion-item">
							<h2 class="mb-0">
								<button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">Pioneering Achievements</button>
							</h2>
							<div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordion_1">
								<div class="accordion-body">
									Starting in a modest clinic in Alexandria, Dr. Ghalwash introduced revolutionary microsurgical techniques, including toe-to-thumb transfers and complex nerve reconstructions. His dedication has established new standards in reconstructive surgery.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="accordion-item">
							<h2 class="mb-0">
								<button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">Hair Restoration Excellence</button>
							</h2>
							<div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordion_1">
								<div class="accordion-body">
									In the early 1990s, Dr. Ghalwash pioneered follicular unit transplantation in Saudi Arabia, revolutionizing hair restoration with meticulous attention to natural hairline design and patient satisfaction.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="accordion-item">
							<h2 class="mb-0">
								<button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">Microsurgical Innovation</button>
							</h2>
							<div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordion_1">
								<div class="accordion-body">
									Using precision instruments and advanced techniques, Dr. Ghalwash has performed over 2,300 successful replantations and reconstructions. His 24/7 dedication to emergency cases has saved countless limbs and restored function to severely injured patients.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	{{> footer}}

	<script src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/tiny-slider.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/aos.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/navbar.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/counter.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/glightbox.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/custom.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

	<script>
		document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
			const infoElement = document.getElementById('info');
			const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
				(entries, observer) => {
					entries.forEach(entry => {
						if (entry.isIntersecting) {
							entry.target.classList.add('active');
							observer.unobserve(entry.target);
						}
					});
				},
				{
					threshold: 0.1
				}
			);
			if (infoElement) {
				observer.observe(infoElement);
			}
		});
	</script>
</body>
</html>